room_title: Escape room "Pirates - The Wicked Ship" by LOCKED in New York
room_description: You and your team are wandering in an old Caribbean harbor full of Pirates. The stories that reach your ears talk about lost ships and hidden treasures that haunt the area.A stranger passes by and asks you to follow him. He walks towards a dark and mysterious ship in the mist. Did he choose you randomly? Will you trust him?
